node.title: Mt Roskill homicide that left man dead, two others in hospital 'not a random attack'
node.description: Det Insp Scott Beard revealed one of the attackers wielded a machete during the home invasion.
node.content: ["Police have revealed the Mt Roskill home invasion that left a man dead and two others in hospital was \"not a random attack\".", "Police were notified of the incident at an address on Glass Rd, Mt Roskill, at about 9:30pm on Thursday.\u00a0", "Det Insp Scott Beard revealed at a press-conference on Friday that one of the attackers wielded a machete during the home invasion.", "More to come."]
